<TEXT>This SUV is actually fun to drive. Plenty of pep for a 6 cylinder. The car is smooth as silk. My wife loves the rear view camera. I love the overall comfort.</TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Backup camera. Built in navigation. Sirius radio</FAVORITE>
